Class Question

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zelvator.questions.Question

  • public class Question
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used for storing attributes from the child nodes within question node in the xml file. Answers could be N, and they could be correct and wrong, so that's why it is in the List of Answer objects.
